I know we talked a little bit before you came on, and I thought maybe you could just

00:01:55.760 --> 00:02:01.000
catch us up on your career, starting with your love of text adventures.

00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:02.000
Oh, yes.

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:03.000
Maybe we could go there and-

